{"tid":1824712,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和理非有一個好好好重要嘅技能係需要大家學習，但好多手足都極度缺乏","createTime":"2020-01-14T15:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T08:23:39.000Z","uid":1477,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79c78ddd92ecbc79d5dbcfe1bf8e00bed5a412f1","tid":1824712,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"咁其實都七個月啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家都應該要搵d 新方法黎主動黎搵資訊</span></span><br />\n而唔係人地塞傳單你先睇<br />\n唔係人地facebook foward 你先like<br />\n唔係人地airdrop 文宣你先知<br />\n<br />\n我知<br />\n我明白<br />\n我理解<br />\n有好多人都係需要人地提供資訊先得<br />\n但如果你覺得自己可以做多一步嘅話<br />\n咁你就試下建立一個方法<br />\n比自己可以主動吸引資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">例如你可以試下用呢個網</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=0b4dbeea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OfK8fzd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfK8fzd.png&h=af95d0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">介面簡單，一次過show 哂當日有咩行動<br />\n仲可以㩒一個制就知未來幾日有咩行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實只係一個網站就可以比你好快速咁知道黎緊有咩行動<br />\n如果你覺得自己可以做多一步嘅<br />\n咁我希望你可以踏出呢一步<br />\n主動呢個網，睇下有咩行動<br />\n然後自己係facebook, instragam, twitter, whatsapp, telegram 到呼籲<br />\n我地唔係需要邊個邊個幫手<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係需要你幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好心一啲人啦<br />\n廿幾歲人，好唔好意思話而家睇唔到有文宣<br />\n所以唔知有咩行動<br />\n屌你當手足嘅文宣係tvb廣告？<br />\ndraw 到你attention 先叫成功文宣？<br />\n你問心有無主動search 下抗爭嘅野？<br />\n你要買野都識上淘寶search 下有無平野啦<br />\n點解抗爭嘅野就係靠網上嘅「廣告」？<br />\n無撚野下話<br />\n連抗爭都要做free rider?<br />\n屌你老尾<br />\n利申：分化狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a5323f411571e3d25dcd75535112c21d224dcac","tid":1824712,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"禮拜五講座，手足們唔該幫推置頂<br />\n<br />\n【行動post】【吳敏兒和你組工會】1月17日（五）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"50f71330d79c84f463606744fee433bae6027d6d","tid":1824712,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e0ac5b37cfca2eb9034cb95bff11cba599271e6","tid":1824712,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣材料唔應該只局限於「紙」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85b25ed7eb725aee0390a9fc951f7acb193fc6cf","tid":1824712,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c78ddd92ecbc79d5dbcfe1bf8e00bed5a412f1","tid":1824712,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"咁其實都七個月啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家都應該要搵d 新方法黎主動黎搵資訊</span></span><br />\n而唔係人地塞傳單你先睇<br />\n唔係人地facebook foward 你先like<br />\n唔係人地airdrop 文宣你先知<br />\n<br />\n我知<br />\n我明白<br />\n我理解<br />\n有好多人都係需要人地提供資訊先得<br />\n但如果你覺得自己可以做多一步嘅話<br />\n咁你就試下建立一個方法<br />\n比自己可以主動吸引資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">例如你可以試下用呢個網</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=0b4dbeea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a