"color: gold;\">介面簡單，一次過show 哂當日有咩行動<br />\n仲可以㩒一個制就知未來幾日有咩行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實只係一個網站就可以比你好快速咁知道黎緊有咩行動<br />\n如果你覺得自己可以做多一步嘅<br />\n咁我希望你可以踏出呢一步<br />\n主動呢個網，睇下有咩行動<br />\n然後自己係facebook, instragam, twitter, whatsapp, telegram 到呼籲<br />\n我地唔係需要邊個邊個幫手<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地係需要你幫手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好心一啲人啦<br />\n廿幾歲人，好唔好意思話而家睇唔到有文宣<br />\n所以唔知有咩行動<br />\n屌你當手足嘅文宣係tvb廣告？<br />\ndraw 到你attention 先叫成功文宣？<br />\n你問心有無主動search 下抗爭嘅野？<br />\n你要買野都識上淘寶search 下有無平野啦<br />\n點解抗爭嘅野就係靠網上嘅「廣告」？<br />\n無撚野下話<br />\n連抗爭都要做free rider?<br />\n屌你老尾<br />\n利申：分化狗</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"（推熱門）用你一分鐘睇已經幫到呢場革命好多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677196</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一早講過了，不過唔知幾多人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a793f23846d985e724b2343ee33cc2ffdd27f6e","tid":1824712,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"【第廿貳期牆紙】 為良知發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=99ba841e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=5dc88761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"ht